headline.print_headline: CDC Sees Low Ebola Risk in Passengers Pulled From Dubai Flight
headline.main: CDC Sees Low Ebola Risk in Passengers Pulled From Dubai Flight

lead_paragraph: Emergency crews in protective gear removed five passengers with flu-like symptoms from a commercial airliner that arrived at Boston's Logan Airport from Dubai on Monday, but U.S. health authorities said the possibility of Ebola was "exceedingly low."
